item.title: Win a Free Party for 6
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: Ask your guests to drop their cards in a box for a drawing for a party of 6 of their friends. Offer to make appetizers (inexpensive for you) and give them a discount on the booze. This helps you build your list, but also gets you new potential customers that your guest has invited.

item.title: Live Music
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: Speaking of chord! Local musicians are always looking for a place to play. Why not dedicate one night to “Jazz Night” or “Live DJ”? Then print out table tents touting this new night! Send a weekly email to announce who will be there that week.
